{"id":100,"name":"العاديات","transliteration":"Al-'Adiyat","translation":"奔驰的马队","type":"meccan","total_verses":11,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"وَٱلۡعَٰدِيَٰتِ ضَبۡحٗا","translation":"以喘息而奔驰的马队盟誓，","transliteration":"WaalAAadiyati dabhan"},{"id":2,"text":"فَٱلۡمُورِيَٰتِ قَدۡحٗا","translation":"以蹄发火花的马队盟誓，","transliteration":"Faalmooriyati qadhan"},{"id":3,"text":"فَٱلۡمُغِيرَٰتِ صُبۡحٗا","translation":"以早晨出击，","transliteration":"Faalmugheerati subhan"},{"id":4,"text":"فَأَثَرۡنَ بِهِۦ نَقۡعٗا","translation":"卷起尘埃，","transliteration":"Faatharna bihi naqAAan"},{"id":5,"text":"فَوَسَطۡنَ بِهِۦ جَمۡعًا","translation":"攻入敌围的马队盟誓，","transliteration":"Fawasatna bihi jamAAan"},{"id":6,"text":"إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٞ","translation":"人对于主, 确是孤负的。","transliteration":"Inna alinsana lirabbihi lakanoodun"},{"id":7,"text":"وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٞ","translation":"他自己对那孤负确是见证的，","transliteration":"Wainnahu AAala thalika lashaheedun"},{"id":8,"text":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لِحُبِّ ٱلۡخَيۡرِ لَشَدِيدٌ","translation":"他对于财产确是酷好的。","transliteration":"Wainnahu lihubbi alkhayri lashadeedun"},{"id":9,"text":"۞أَفَلَا يَعۡلَمُ إِذَا بُعۡثِرَ مَا فِي ٱلۡقُبُورِ","translation":"难道他不知道吗？当坟中的朽骨被揭发，","transliteration":"Afala yaAAlamu itha buAAthira ma fee alquboori"},{"id":10,"text":"وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِي ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"胸中的秘密被显示的时候，","transliteration":"Wahussila ma fee alssudoori"},{"id":11,"text":"إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّخَبِيرُۢ","translation":"在那日，他们的主，确是彻知他们的。","transliteration":"Inna rabbahum bihim yawmaithin lakhabeerun"}]}
